{
  "stem": "24163.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just didn't have much to say to them, except I wanted to see the apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At the time when we moved in, it was a brand new building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But by that time, it looked sort of grimy to me, and-- I, I, yeah, I did see it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my primary purpose there also, then, was to go to the grave site of my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my-- besides visiting, I mean, trying to capture this SOB, I visited my mother's grave site, I visited my brother's grave site, uncles, aunts, cousins, people who were in the Jewish cemeteries in either Essen or Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spent an entire day doing that the next day, before I went back to my unit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were in terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They claimed-- and the tombstones had been turned over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they claimed, the German authority claimed a lot of this was due to bomb damage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of it might have been.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I would say that most of the headstones looked to me like they had been turned over, physically, by vandals, I would think, by-- my mother's gravestone had been turned upside down.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I knew exactly where it was located, so I found it immediately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the grass was overgrown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, nobody had taken care of the cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It looked awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a soul, not-- I'm trying to think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When later on, many, many, many years later, we once went to France, my wife and I.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we also visited Germany for the second time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I spoke to several people, including some Jews who had moved back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was-- there were two survivors that I-- no, three survivors of the original German Jewish community in Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
